    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You owe the mafia some money...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In &quot;Pew Pew Gaem 3&quot; you fight trough deadly waves of enemies trying to escape them and also trying to find who's behind this seeking revenge...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here's some cool features in this game!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bunny hopping</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaning</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Takedown System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stealth system</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is Story levels:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Warehouse</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Port</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sea</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >House</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forest</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mansion</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >there are 4 Sandbox levels:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grass</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Moon</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Construct</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blaeu VS Baed</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Theres also 2 maps for the survival/wave gamemode:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GrassSpace</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Snow World</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Theres also a defense mode on one map:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Castle</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hope u enjoy my little game i made and more will be coming soon!</p>",
